ğŸ” Overview

clear_my_record_backend is a secure, intelligent, and automated backend service designed to assist with criminal record expungement, clemency, or record sealing requests via integrated court systems.

This stack is designed to run on private cloud, on-premise, or edge devices (Termux / Raspberry Pi), with optional KermitAGIâ„¢, RedHawkSecureLabâ„¢, and Crown Listenerâ„¢ biometric intelligence enhancements.

